content.rendered:
Last Friday, Margot Hiemstra and Joost Commissaris have successful completed their internship at Corekees. Despite all the working from home, they have managed to develop from students to future professionals. Their succesors are waiting to start their journey.

Hargot and Joco, thankyou a lot and good luck!
